   I've been following this thread since Gelroos told me what happened in a tell.  Now I've grouped with ALOT of different people on this server, both good and bad.  I also feel kinda stuck in the middle because I am friends with member of Bow and Gelroos.<br>
   Do I believe that Gelroos stole these items?  No.<br>
   Do I think that Gelroos is at fault.  Kinda, like alot of other people here, I think he should have more careful with those passwords.  Hell, he probably should have tossed them out, but that's neither here no there.  <br>
   Do I think that Gelroos has had an EXEMPLRY reputation until this happened?   Yes, never heard a bad word about him.<br>
<br>
  I think that everyone involved should take a step back, take a DEEP breath and talk things over like an adult.  I have grouped with BoW MANY a time, and have been impressed by them.  Sure, people can have bad days or may be to busy to reply to 'n00b_01' about how much something is worth, or what the stats are on something, but that's no reason to start flaming BoW in general on something like this, it simply clouds the issue at hand.<br>
  I really feel bad for Kenar, because he is a very nice guy and what happened REALLY sucked.  Sorry bud.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
  By the same token, I feel bad for Gelroos, because one of his friends did this to him.  Like anyone who's ever played for any length of time, and isn't a tool, knows that money, loot and levels come and go... but rep is everything, and Gel's is really screwed right now.  He considered the person a friend and they in turn screwed him.<br>
<br>
That's my two cents,<br>
Ranath Starsword<br>
